      "content": {
        "title": "Knee Joint Biomechanics and Arthropathy — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Knee kinematics, load distribution, and arthropathies including osteoarthritis, inflammatory arthritis, and post-traumatic degeneration.",
        "summary": "Varus and valgus alignment alter compartment loading. Knee OA management progresses from conservative care to arthroplasty based on severity and alignment."
      },
